Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:07.22,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N14
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近校内的风纪变得有些乱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望担任学生辅导的樱井老师能更加严格地监管
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我正是为了改变自己才来担任学生辅导老师的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须好好地监管！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况  这突然出现的是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不行  我绝不能就这样退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边走边吃是不是稍微有失礼节…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈  失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有吃早饭  所以肚子就突然嘶鸣起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就撤掉  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能理解就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  只要和他好好说还是懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我传达下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上发出这么大的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考虑一下学校风纪行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  把那个带来学校的有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美里  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原  午休的时候我有点话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖给我待在教室里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  风纪是有点变乱了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬  立花美里她是没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么  你脖子前那轻飘飘的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  感觉有点可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在日常生活中度过的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上也许是连续发生的奇迹也说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  就是那种东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个  那轻飘飘的到底是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗  哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎扯啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么女士  有机会的话我们课堂上见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:49.88,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be100\3c&HFFFFFF&}学\N生\N辅\N导
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交换着看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  打扰一下  中之条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校留这种发型是不是稍微有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是有点  只是有点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  要是没听清我再重复一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边的…两边的长不出来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:29.87,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,350)\fad(600,600)\bord15\shad0\be100\3c&HFFFFFF&}围\N棋\N足\N球\N部\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:30.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本小孩玩扮鬼游戏时念的咒语「ダルマさんが転んだ」  相当于一二三木头人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁它…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌倒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:40.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请再往前一千步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:45.62,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(600,600)}日\N常\N之\N15
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是青梅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在家里做梅干试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅干…咸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅子对身体有益处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且加在饭团里  饭不容易坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀！  名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是买了一大堆点心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把那些好好吃完  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了之后再来买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哟  今天已经和黑猫先生…叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  约好了买阪本先生的食物回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  请问您有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个  这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是雪人  今天上架的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您喜欢的话  请购买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看起来像是刨冰的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要买吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我…我只是看一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那不是雪人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个如果不买的话就给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我买
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  名乃明明就可以买自己想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士就要的就说「不行」！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不   因为这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃可以买自己想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士想买的东西也能买！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要  我想要  我就要嘛我就要！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}我知道了  就只买一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢名乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就买了这种东西回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很可爱  而且冰冰凉的感觉也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  盛好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  再给我点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你们这帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我的饭在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:38.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}又是5-7-5的俳句格式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这顿饭是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又冰又凉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随口说说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许乱出哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认输…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发条！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
