Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:44.28,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}两\N个\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:48.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道  不对  是单相思
